METALS BANK & TRUST COMPANY, a Corporation, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6131. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 30, 1931.

Before RUDKIN, WILBUR, and SAW-TELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to praecipe of counsel for appellant, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
